Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
380 Victoria Road is a fully leased investment property with two new 10-year leases, located in the heart of the highly sought-after industrial precinct of Malaga.
   
The property is improved with some 8,435sqm* of office/warehouse improvements situated on a 1.51Ha landholding, within proximity to the recently upgraded Reid/Tonkin Highway intersection.  

This is a fantastic long-term investment opportunity with attractive rental increases and future re-positioning or subdivision potential. 

KEY FEATURES:
•	Improvements: 8,435sqm*
•	Land Area: 15,113sqm*
•	100 metre* frontage to Victoria Road
•	National tenant
•	Established Industrial Area
•	Proximity to Malaga Drive and Reid/Tonkin Highways
•	Dual Crossovers
•	Wash Bay (under construction)
•	Hardstand laydown
•	Multiple Tenant Diversity 
•	Zoned “General Industrial”
•	13km* to Perth CBD
•	15km* to Perth Airport

LEASE SUMMARY
•	Anchored by Kresta Holdings Limited 
•	WALE of 9.89 Years* (on income)
•	Combined net income of $599,590 pa

This investment benefits from a strong lease covenant, attractive rental increases and is underpinned by a well improved significant landholding located within the highly sought-after industrial precinct of Malaga.  

For a copy of the information memorandum or to arrange a viewing, please contact the exclusive selling agents.

*approx
